de.mdelab.simulator.mrubis.injectors

Class PI3_Injector

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mdelab.simulator.mrubis.injectors.Abstract_PI_Injector
      • de.mdelab.simulator.mrubis.injectors.PI3_Injector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Injector<Tenant>

    public class PI3_Injector
extends Abstract_PI_Injector
implements Injector<Tenant>
    Injects a PI3 by changing the PerformanceStats of the personalized search within the given Tenant so that the average response time of the search is below the given threshold. The personalized search is provided by the method MRubisNames.getPersonalizedItems_Signature of the interface MRubisNames.browseCategoriesService_InterfaceType_FqName.
    Version:
    0.41
    Author:
    thomas vogel
